review_text: Great place for dogs and humans to relax, work out, picnic, or play pétanque. The park has been recently renovated and it's well maintained. There are regular yoga classes provided by the city during the summer time as well. This is a lovely little urban oasis.
Great little dog park by day and crusing by night. Its to bad it was closed all summer for renovations. Looking forward to see what they do.
Parc moderne et bien entretenue avec 3 terrains de pétanque, des barres de fitness, de multiples table de pic-niques et une fontaine à eau. Parfait pour une soirée pétanque entre amis
